  "title": "M&E Coordinator, Main Contractor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><p>To supervise & coordinator M&E work on site.</p><p>Coordination of sub-contractor's M&E work and ensuring the work is on</p><p>schedule.</p><p>Ensure M&E works are carried out according to specifications / drawings for</p><p>Electrical, ACMV, Plumbing, Sanitary & Fire protection etc.</p><p>Ensure contractor comply with all necessary standards, code of practice and</p><p>safety regulations.</p><p>Arrange and facilitate RE/RTO inspections.</p><p>To liaise with authorities for the commission of work.</p><p>Attend site meeting as and when required Requirements.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>Degree/Diploma in Mechanical Engineering recognised by Singapore</p><p>Professional Engineers Board (PEB) or equivalent with 3 to 5 years of working</p><p>experience in local construction industry.</p><p>Required Skill(s): Autocad, Microsoft Office</p>",
