    "uen": "198401377W",
    "description": "<p>V3 Construction Pte Ltd was established in 1984 as a general building contractor. Founded by its Director, Mr Michael Yap, V3 has grown from a small construction firm to one of the more established construction firms in Singapore. Its capabilities include construction expertise in Residential, Hospitality, Institutional, Commercial and Industrial projects.</p>\n<p>V3 is equally adept at handling both small and large projects. From Luxury Bungalow project, Educational Institution to Hospitality project, V3 applies the same Company Values and adapts itself to achieving the best possible deliverables for the Client.</p>\n<p>Besides construction projects, V3 also takes on Design and Build projects. From design concepts and proposals, to the finished construction, V3 provides one-stop solutions for all Developers' needs.</p>\n<p>The basic philosophy of V3 has always been about quality. Quality in services, products and project management. V3's priority is meeting the objectives and exceeding the high standards set by its Clients and the Firm itself.</p>\n<p>The firm is committed to developing the optimum solution for each project and strives to achieve simplicity, economy and aesthetics, while maintaining the highest professional standards, environmental concerns and responsiveness to Client's needs.</p>",
